FBIS3-7906 "dreeu040__a94022" FBIS-EEU-94-040-A Document Type:Daily Report 1 March 1994 ANNEX Romania Iliescu Condemns `Irresponsible Act' in Hebron AU2602165194 Bucharest ROMPRES in English 1526 GMT 26 Feb 94 AU2602165194 Bucharest ROMPRES Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Bucharest, ROMPRES 26/2/1994 -- Romania's President Ion Iliescu has sent a telegram of condolence to Yasir `Arafat, president of the state of Palestine, president of the Executive Committee of the PLO, in which he firmly condemns "the criminal and irresponsible act committed in Hebron, Cisjordan." "We express our conviction that the Palestinian people and the PLO leadership would know how to overcome this sad and dramatic moment of hard trial and sufferings, honouring the memory of the Palestinian martyrs in Hebron by new efforts and active demarches to further the process of peace in the Middle East," the telegram reads.
